spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Infrastructure\\SymfonyAi"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\SymfonyAi"
updatedAt: 2026-04-22
description: "Symfony AI bridge — adapters connecting the agent loop to the Symfony AI ecosystem (platform, tool executor, message mapping, streaming)."
files[5]{file,type,summary}:
  Platform.php,readonly final class,"Orchestrates AI provider calls by resolving context, mapping messages, applying hooks, and delegating invocation to the platform adapter."
  RunCancellationToken.php,readonly final class,Checks whether a run has been cancelled by querying the run store on demand.
  StreamDeltaReducer.php,final class,"Reduces streaming AI response deltas into a final assistant message with text content, tool calls, and usage statistics."
  SymfonyMessageMapper.php,final class,"Converts between internal AgentMessage objects and Symfony AI provider message formats, handling tool-call serialization."
  SymfonyPlatformInvoker.php,readonly final class,Invokes the Symfony AI platform model endpoint and extracts structured usage metadata from deferred results.